      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/39/738",
      "text": [
        " اَلْمَحْمِلِ فَقَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ بِالصَّلاَةِ عَلَيْهَا."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.738 – Zurarah asked Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about a cushion (shadhakunah) that may have come into contact with major ritual impurity (janabah) and whether it is permissible to pray on it while it is in a carriage (mahmil).\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in praying on it.\""
        ]
      }
    },
